reviewText: I love this video!  I first started doing Dancerobics about 20 years ago, and it's the only workout that I have stuck to, and do consistently!  I am now, also, doing the Pilates, "Body Victory" DVDs.  Thank you, Marilu!  You've created a workout that is fun and challenging, but easy to follow!
My sisters and I used to own this many years ago when I was a kid. I lost it, so I was determined to get another copy.  You will break a sweat, but there is also a low impact option available.

Marilu did not think about the people with two left feet. She goes really fast during the dance steps. I could not even do half of the workout when I did it for the first time. She does not realize that not everyone could do the dances that she does in the video
